{"tid":1198570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"二零一九年六月十二日 屬於香港人嘅End Game","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T09:26:28.000Z","uid":163199,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"675273e8230679184468e9c234a20da7907c056f","tid":1198570,"uid":163199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:22:54.000Z","msg":"六月九日 上演咗屬於香港人嘅Infinity War<br />\n103萬人上街示威 林鄭依舊厚面皮<br />\n深夜時分先出聲明表示會照推二讀<br />\n留守嘅香港人一聽到消息就想衝擊立法會<br />\n可惜準備唔夠 俾警犬撳住打<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊星期三<br />\n六月十二日<br />\n係最後嘅機會<br />\n只有一次<br />\n麻煩大家一齊集結<br />\n創造歷史<br />\n向港共政權作出反擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://qph.fs.quoracdn.net/main-qimg-4f7da5c06abe196babfc59e2fa10666e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqph.fs.quoracdn.net%2Fmain-qimg-4f7da5c06abe196babfc59e2fa10666e&h=b28d101b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f67aff1d5071d5cf3a75f7f5878d3b555c725f05","tid":1198570,"uid":67229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:26:28.000Z","msg":"唔接好意思 阻你少少位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實好多外國人對香港發生緊嘅野都好關心<br />\n外國嘅網上輿論都對佢地政府嘅表態有好大影響<br />\n或者最少都有多d記者見到網上咁多人討論而去增加報導<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要集合連登各位鍵盤戰士嘅力量 一齊集中火力都去幾個重要反送中嘅post 一定可以係reddit上到熱門 引到佢地討論</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係如果大家唔係集中係一個post入面就好難可以推到上front page <br />\n而令到更多人討論同關注反送中<br />\n尋日我見到都有好多巴打係reddit開post<br />\n好慶幸有幾個上左reddit 熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>69遊行成為reddit史上最多人正評圖片之一</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1197068\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1197068</a><br />\n<br />\n好似依個post咁 成功係reddit引到好多鬼佬討論<br />\n<br />\n所以如果可以集整連登巴打嘅力量 <br />\n一齊upvote將幾個重要嘅post推上front page<br />\n好過分散咁開post<br />\n依一樣係最少所有鍵盤戰士都可以做嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<ins>有reddit 嘅一齊上 冇嘅快d上去注冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/register/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fregister%2F&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=fed02fb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reddit.com/register/</a></ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Tg group</span></strong>: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MxGPJBS_xbcGH5J5EmX1lQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMxGPJBS_xbcGH5J5EmX1lQ&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=f3f5b390\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MxGPJBS_xbcGH5J5EmX1lQ</a>"}]}